"Formulaires multi-étapes avec scoring de leads, double opt-in conforme, "
"notifications bilingues et insertion par shortcode, sans aucune extension "
"supplémentaire."
msgstr ""
"Multi-step forms with lead scoring, compliant double opt-in, bilingual "
"notifications and shortcode insertion, without any extra plugin."

